---
group_count: 53
atr1_unknown: 4
entries:
  Atacked00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 42
      - text: 雖想騎馬逃走，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n但現在是否該按兵不動……"
  Atacked01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 42
      - text: 事情變棘手了……
  Failed00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 討人厭的怪物已經不在了嗎？
  Failed01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 真擔心我的愛馬……
  Guardian00:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 31
      - text: 逃啊！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 衝啊！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n快逃離"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 守護者
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ！
  MSG_Kyu_00:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 我的旅行中不可或缺的，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n你覺得是什麼？\n那就是"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "馬。\n\n只要馬還在，就算我自己不在了也無所謂，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n馬對我的旅行來說，就是這麼重要。"
  MSG_Kyu_00_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 我的旅行中不可或缺的，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n那就是馬。"
  MSG_Kyu_01:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 6
      - text: 嗯？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 怎麼了？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n啊，這樣啊，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "想問我有關馬的事嗎？\n哎，不用客氣！"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n只要是有關馬的事，要我說多少都沒問題！\n比方說，稱讚馬的正確方法，\n就像這樣……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 馬乖乖聽話時，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 就輕輕拍牠以示獎勵，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n馬努力奔跑時，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 也輕輕拍牠以示獎勵。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 這就是稱讚馬的時機，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 記住了嗎？
  MSG_Kyu_01_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 馬乖乖聽話時
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 就輕輕拍牠以示獎勵，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n馬努力奔跑時，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 也輕輕拍牠以示獎勵。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 這就是稱讚馬的時機，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 記住了嗎？
  MSG_Kyu_02:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 向我搭話是無所謂啦，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n但我是個只有馬的話題可聊的男人喔？\n比方說，馬在緊要關頭也會游泳，\n這點你知道嗎？\n不知道其他動物會不會游，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n不過馬確實算是會游！"
  MSG_Kyu_02_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 6
      - text: "馬在緊要關頭也會游泳，\n這點你知道嗎？"
  MSG_Kyu_03:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "我是個不管跟誰聊，都以馬的話題起頭的男人，\n這點你最好先知道。\n世界上雖有無數驛站，但我接下來要說的這幾個，\n可會幫人配上別具一格的韁繩和馬鞍喔！\n聽好，可要記住啊……\n\n森林驛站、高原驛站、平原外圍的驛站"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n還有南阿卡萊驛站"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: ……就是以上四個。
  MSG_Kyu_03_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "會幫人配上別具一格的\n韁繩和馬鞍的驛站，共有四個……\n森林驛站、高原驛站、平原外圍的驛站"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n還有南阿卡萊驛站"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: ……就是這些。
  MSG_Kyu_04:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "我非常喜歡馬，\n喜歡得甚至想說，我愛馬愛到骨子裡了。\n說到骨就想到，我曾在積滿雪的深山裡\n遇過只有骨頭的馬。\n你問那恐不恐怖？\n我並不是要說恐怖故事。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: "那隻骨馬實在跑得很好，\n而且騎起來的感覺也很不錯喔！"
  MSG_Kyu_04_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: "我曾在積滿雪的深山裡遇過骨馬。\n騎起來的感覺比想像中還好喔。"
  Near00:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - text: 胡蘿蔔……
  Near01:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - text: 用滑翔傘接近馬……
  Near02:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - text: 沒事沒事……
  Near03:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - text: 才沒什麼機械馬……
  Near04:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - text: 嘶嘶～！
  Rest_00:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "我是個說馬說個不停，結果讓\n老婆跑掉的男人，找我什麼事？\n對了，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 告訴你一件好消息吧。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n有點難記，你可要加油啊。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 在初始台地的西北方有座薩托利山……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n在它東邊的撒丁公園遺跡附近……\n有非常適合王子騎乘的馬喔。"
  Rest_01:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "下雨天真閒，那我就來出個馬的謎語吧。\n\n白馬……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 巨大的馬……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 機械馬……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 骨馬……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n來，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 哪種才是這世上不存在的馬？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 正確答案，總有一天我會在哪裡公布，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n而且搞不好已經公布過了喔。"
  Rest_02:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 16
      - text: "下馬啦……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 說錯了！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n是下雨啦！"
  RetMSG_Kyu_00:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 話先說在前頭，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "若想從我這裡問出\n馬以外的資訊，你還是死心吧。\n話說女孩子啊，總會滿臉憧憬地\n說白馬王子如何又如何啦……\n我倒是希望有白馬來迎接我，\n上面不用載什麼王子啦。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 馬有各種體色，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: 像斑紋、栗色、黑色……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n但每當我看見白馬，還是忍不住屏息啊。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_00_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 馬有各種體色，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: 像斑紋、栗色、黑色……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n但每當我看見白馬，還是忍不住屏息啊。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_01:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 我很不擅長跟人溝通，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n但假如是馬，起碼我就有自信能心意相通。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 18
      - text: 假如是馬，起碼……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n這可不是雙關語喔，只是偶然同音而已。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 1
      - text: 要好好駕馭馬匹，就要能跟牠溝通。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n想做到這點，就要增加騎馬的時間。\n……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 2
            - 4
      - text: 剛才那個，真的只是偶然而已啊！
  RetMSG_Kyu_01_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 要好好駕馭馬匹，就要能跟牠溝通。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n想做到這點，就要增加騎馬的時間。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_02:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 我一天中有三分之二的時間都在想馬，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n剩下三分之一則是做馬的夢，找我什麼事？\n對了，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "機會難得，\n我就來說說野生馬的事吧。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 6
      - text: "有些馬只要一靠近牠，就會馬上察覺\n並且跑走，實在很難搞對吧？\n像那種馬啊，\n其實都是能力特別優秀的好馬喔！"
  RetMSG_Kyu_02_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 只要一靠近，就會馬上察覺並且跑走的馬，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n才是能力特別優秀的好馬，好好記住啊！"
  RetMSG_Kyu_03:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 若你想問我海拉魯城堡的事，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n那可就找錯人了。\n我只談馬。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 馬。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "來談馬的事吧。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 就算是野生馬，只要成了愛馬就形同家人。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n而且是跑得快，又願意讓你乘在背上的家人。\n決定愛馬之後，就要先去驛站登錄。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n這也是為了讓牠能一直陪著你啊。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_03_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 就算是野生馬，只要成了愛馬就形同家人。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n為了長久陪伴彼此，就要先去驛站登錄。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_04:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 我只要一談起馬，就會變得很長舌喔！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n而且會比馬臉還要長喔，你可要有心理準備啊。\n這馬鞍是我自豪的馬具，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n無論是和馬背或我的屁股，都非常搭。\n而且韁繩也非常好握，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n既柔韌又好操控。\n只要去驛站將野生馬登錄成自己的馬，"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n驛站就會幫你配好馬鞍與韁繩，這你知道吧？\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 我說完了。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n倒沒有想像中長啊。"
  RetMSG_Kyu_04_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 只要去驛站將野生馬登錄成自己的馬，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n驛站就會幫你配好馬鞍與韁繩，這你知道吧？"
  SavedLv1_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 看來總算得救啦！
  SavedLv1_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 看來已經沒事啦！
  SavedLv2_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 2
      - text: 救了我的……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: 就是你嗎？
  SavedLv2_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: 要是被怪物襲擊，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n騎馬逃跑還是最好的……"
  SavedLv3_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 我一到緊要關頭就什麼也辦不到……
  SavedLv3_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 我的計畫就是騎馬逃走……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: 本來是啦。
  Thanks00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 9
      - text: 這是一點小謝禮！
